<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN210">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>maṉpatai kākkuniṉ puraimai nōkkā</l>
<l>taṉpukaṇ māṟiya vaṟaṉil kāṭciyoṭu</l>
<l>numma ṉōrumaṟ ṟiṉaiya rāyi</l>
<l>ṉemma ṉōrivaṭ piṟavalar mātō</l>
<l>ceyirtīr koḷkai yemveṅ kātali</l>
<l>yuyirciṟi tuṭaiya ḷāyi ṉemvayi</l>
<l>ṉuḷḷā tiruttalō varitē yataṉā</l>
<l>laṟaṉil kūṟṟan tiṟaṉiṉṟu tuṇiyap</l>
<l>piṟaṉā yiṉaṉko liṟīiyareṉ ṉuyireṉa</l>
<l>nuvalvuṟu ciṟumaiyaḷ palapulan tuṟaiyu</l>
<l>miṭukkaṇ maṉaiyō ṭīriya vinnilai</l>
<l>viṭuttaṉaṉ vāḻiyar kuruci lutukkā</l>
<l>ṇavala neñcamoṭu celvaṉiṟ kaṟuttō</l>
<l>raruṅkaṭi muṉaiyaraṇ pōlap</l>
<l>peruṅkai yaṟṟaveṉ pulampumun tuṟuttē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Not looking at your greatness that guards humanity, (1)</l>
<l>with virtueless sight that has changed from love, (2) </l>
<l>if the likes of you are like this (3)</l>
<l>should the likes of us be born here? (4)</l>
<l>The beloved who is keen on us, with blemishless principles, (5)</l>
<l>if she possesses a life that is small, without thinking</l>
<l>about us, as for living [on], that is difficult. Therefore (6f.)</l>
<l>“When the power of virtueless Death is determined today, (8)</l>
<l>has he become another (~ is he dead)? May my life break”, (9)</l>
<l>with a despondency that experienced talking [of that kind] she remains much vexed. (10)</l>
<l>So that the affliction of her in the house ends, from this position (11)</l>
<l>I take leave. Live [long]. lord – see here: (12)</l>
<l>I go with a heavy heart, (13a-c)</l>
<l>placing before me my loneliness that is greatly prostrate, (15)</l>
<l>like a fortress on the heavily guarded frontier of those who angered you. (13d-14)  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
